Description: This crate provides for serialization/deserialization of NETLINK SOCK DIAG
messages. It is used by Starnix to serve the NETLINK protocol.
Local Modifications: This crate forks upstream version 0.4.2. There are several divergences from
upstream (See the git history for the complete list). At this point, there is
no intention of re-merging with upstream.
